o  september  ebay’s paypal acquires payments gateway braintree for m in cash techcrunch retrieved  november    jillian donfro june   paypal president david marcus is stepping down to join facebook business insider   a b tricia duryee march   ebay promotes david marcus to fill top vacancy at paypal allthingsdcom dow jones retrieved october     a b cromwell schubarth  september  meet paypal ceotobe schulman homelessness exercise as a management tool silicon valley business journal retrieved  november    de la merced michael sorkin andrew ebay to spin off paypal adopting strategy backed by icahn the new york times retrieved  september    mukherjee supantha ebay follows icahns advice plans paypal spinoff in  reuters retrieved  september    cheng roger ebay paypal to split into separate companies in  cnet retrieved  september    paypal acquires money transfer firm xoom for  million fortune retrieved    wingfield nick  paypal acquires xoom for stake in digital money transfers the new york times issn  retrieved    a b c perez sarah paypal launches paypalme a simpler way to request money using your own personalized url tech crunch retrieved  september    brian matt paypal makes it even easier to call in your debts engadget retrieved  september    here are the  new companies joining the fortune  fortunecom  retrieved    a b c d e f g h i j paypal  acquisitions  crunchbase wwwcrunchbasecom retrieved    ebay acquires bill me later for almost  billion  finovate finovate  retrieved    rao leena ebay acquires locationbased media and advertising company where  techcrunch retrieved    rao leena ebays paypal buys mobile payments startup fig card  techcrunch retrieved    mcmahan ty  ebay’s zong deal mobile payments are all fun  games wsj retrieved    nathan donatoweinstein  january  fastgrowing ebay spreads out in north san jose san jose business journal retrieved  november    a b josh funk  june  paypal center in lavista moves online payments worldwide journalstar retrieved  novemb