tform and digital payments company that enables digital and mobile payments on behalf of consumers and merchants the companys combined payment solutions including its paypal paypal credit braintree venmo xoom and paydiant products compose its payments platform it operates a twosided global technology platform that links its customers both merchants and consumers around the globe to facilitate the processing of payment transactions allowing it to connect merchants and consumers it allows its customers to use their account for both purchase and paying for goods as well as to transfer and withdraw funds it enables consumers to exchange funds with merchants using funding sources which include bank account paypal account balance paypal credit account credit and debit card or other stored value products it offers consumers persontoperson payment solutions through its paypal website and mobile application venmo and xoom receive news  ratings via email  enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts ratings with marketbeatcoms free daily email newsletter leave a reply cancel reply your email address will not be published required fields are marked comment name  email  website more news monarch casino  resort nysemcri target price raised to  issued a report today by imperial capital just yesterday monarch casino  resort a statement released earlier today by scotia capital about premier gold mines limited tsepg bumps the target price to  boasting a price of  premier nutrisystem ndaqntri target price raised to  reported today by lake street yesterday nutrisystem ndaqntri traded  lower plaza retail reit tseplzun stock price target increased to  issued a research note today by laurentian bank in a report released on  a report released today by scotia capital about methanex ndaqmeoh bumps the target price to  just yesterday methanex ndaqmeoh traded  lundin mining tselun target price bumped up to  issued a research note today by b