ass russia  paypal system stops servicing clients in crimea tass retrieved  september    paypal to exit turkey after regulator denies payments license  paypal to halt operations in turkey after losing license impacts ‘hundreds of thousands’   list of country codes where paypal available   paypal brushesoff request from palestinian tech firms to access the platform   httpswwwpaypalcomgivingfundfaq  paypal is not a bank entrepreneurial thought leader speaker series ecorner  january  retrieved  november    chu lenora february   what paypal does with your money cnnmoney retrieved  march    fdic decides paypals no bank zdnet march   retrieved on   bepresscom retrieved january     uniting and strengthening america by providing appropriate tools required to intercept and obstruct terrorism usa patriot act act of  pub l no   stat    a b margaret jane radin et al internet commerce the emerging legal framework – foundation press d ed   article  of the eus banking directive directive ec  paypal obtains bank charter for european union paymentsnewscom retrieved february     stevenson tom paypal becomes a bank to fight off google the daily telegraph retrieved september     paypal becomes a bank no longer under fsa  tamebay  ebay  ecommerce made easy tamebay may   retrieved february     holahan catherine june   businessweekcom bloomberg businessweek retrieved january     fsagovuk fsagovuk retrieved january     nytimescom the new york times indias central bank stops some paypal services by heather timmons and claire cain miller february    rbiorgin certificates of authorisation issued by the reserve bank of india under the payment and settlement systems act  for setting up and operating payment system in india  ebay helpfile on paisapay ebayin help file on paisapay retrieved october     authority to carry on banking business banking act  pdf   kukiewicz julia november   choosenet choosenet retrieved november     miloseskireid paul july   home affairs committee publicationsparliamen